text: Santa Catarina is a municipality. It is on the island of Santiago. The capital city is Assomada. Its mountains, including Serra Malagueta and Pico da Antónia, are the highest of the island.Evolução histórica do Concelho de Santa Catarina (1834 – 1912) , Ana Zenaida Gomes, 2005 ==References== Category:Municipalities of Cape Verde
title: Santa Catarina, Cape Verde
